        "text_bKfTra": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When it comes to wedding jewelry, you should definitely have something special for your big day — and no, I don't just mean the wedding rings! </p><p>You can have your Kaaret custom wedding jewelry made to match your personality, mood, dress or the vision board you probably already have. I work with vintage, secondhand and deadstock materials, including freshwater pearls, silk and glass beads, which I combine with stainless steel components and other materials. Read on and discover the path to your ideal piece. </p><p></p><h4>Want your wedding jewelry from Kaaret?</h4>"
          }
        },
